                                     <strong>Taңғy naryқtaryna sholu 06.02.2020</strong><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><h2><span> Қayyrly kүn!!!</span></h2><p><span></span></p><p><span><i> Sarқylmas optimizm gheteleydі naryқtary. Virus қauіptі emes, bar arbidol, impichment Trampu batyp ketken, senatta AҚSh baruғa dayynbyz beru Қytayғa sauda kelіsіmі. Қayda ghoқ қara – barlyқ gherde ghappay pozitiv. Taң almas investorlar auysady ghaғdayyna, dүrbeleң toқmeyіlsu өndіrіlgen anyқ, bұl kөptegen hedgh қorlar sidyat na "algotreydinge". Bіzdің BҚ ghұma kүnі ponizit stavkany 0.25% eskere otyryp, қanday құmarlyқtyң satylyp ketken keshe OFZ ghәne ghұma kүnі kөremіz derekter boyynsha AҚSh-taғy ghұmyssyzdyқ, bіraқ Tramp қazіrdің өzіnde mәlіmdedі, sonday-aқ ghaқsy Amerikada kezde de, ol eshқashan...</i></span></p><p><span><b>Indeks S&amp;P500 </b></span><span> - Keshe </span><span><b>S&amp;P500 </b></span><span> ghәne </span><span><b>NASDAQ</b></span><span> ghabyldy tarihi maksimumah, al taңerteң fyyucherster osy indeksterі olardy kөshіrіp. Ghaңa maksimumdar, kүtuge ұzaқ uaқyt emes edі. Ralli ghalғasuda.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Bүgіn kүtemіz diapazony </span><span><b>3305 – 3369. </b></span></p><p><span><b>RTS ghәne MMVB</b></span><span> – Tүzetu baғa boyynsha tөmen қaray ayaқtaldy. Kүtemіz kөteru bұrynғy eң ghoғary mәnderі. Stavkasyn tөmendetu, RF ghәne aғyny ghaңa gheke klientterge birghaғa kөmektesuі tiіs indekster өsuі. Әzіrge kөrіnetіn sebepterіn azaytu үshіn ghoқ, deydі ghalғastyru өsu. Aytar bolsaқ, bұl saқ ghәne saқtyқ paydasyz, barlyқ oslepleny ghaghdoy oңay olgha, үlken dividendtіk tөlemderdің өsuіmen baғamdyқ құnynyң қaғazdar ghәne t. b. Әuelde ghay ғana dep aytuғa bolady dividendter tөleu үshіn өtken, 2019 ghyly, ol emes, eң nashar, al nәtighelerі 2020 mүmkіn қatty kөңіlіn investorlar. Tүyіn қoldau bүgіngі taңda ornalasқan fyyucherster boyynsha na </span><span><b>RTS 154300</b></span><span> arnalғan </span><span><b>MMVB 312800</b></span><span>, al kedergіsіn </span><span><b>RTS 158800 </b></span><span>boyynsha</span><span><b> MMVB 316800 .</b></span></p><p><span><b>MҰNAY </b></span><span> – Nefty keshe kөrsettі ghetkіlіktі kүshtі myқtylyқ baғalar boyynsha, ghәne de mұnay men mұnay өnіmderіn өstі, mұnay өndіru deңgeyі AҚSh-ta tөmendedі, </span><span><b>13 mln. deyіn 12.9 mln. barrely</b></span><span>.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Aғymdaғy deңgeyde mұnay, mұnay kompaniyalary emes hedghiruyut өz shikіzat ghetkіzu, sondyқtan қysym azaydy fyyucherstіk kelіsіm-sharttar, әsіrese merzіmіmen, gharty ghylғa ghәne әrі қaray. Tehnikalyқ komitet OPEK bүgіn өz ghұmysyn ghalғastyrady, bіraқ keshe olar ony ayaқtau. Shamasy, bіz OPEK-tің ghәne eresek ghәne koletsya baғasy keletіn kөteru ghәne өndіruge tyrysu emes tөmendetu.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Bұl tұrғyda AҚSh-ta ghәne Kanadada "slanceviki" ghәne "dәstүrlі mұnayshylar" tez ghauap berse, baғa boyynsha mұnay, ghedel қysқarta otyryp nemese arttyru arқyly өndіru. Olardyң eshқanday kartelynye shekteu қatysy ghoқ. Әzіrge mұnay bayқaymyz myқtylyқ baғalardy, onyң қanshalyқty kүshtі kөrsetedі bұl apta. Әzіrge kүtemіz, ghәne bylay dep ghazdy keshe</span><span><b> 58+/- </b></span><span>boyynsha BRENT </span><span><b>54+/- </b></span><span>boyynsha LAYT. </span><span><b>14-15 aқpanda</b></span><span> bolady otyrysy OPEK+, naryқ kүtіp, ghaңa қysқartular өndіru. </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Sauda diapazony mұnay baғasynyң ghөnіndegі </span><span><b>BR-3.20</b></span><span> bүgіn (54,2 </span><span><b>-55,35) – (56,7 – </b></span><span>57,75) boyynsha </span><span><b>CFD</b></span><span> </span><span><b>WTI</b></span><span> </span><span><b>(</b></span><span>49.90</span><span><b> - 50,9) – (52,3 -</b></span><span>53.35</span><span><b>) </b></span></p><p><span><b>Dragmetally – </b></span><span>kezeңі Ghүrіp ghatyr shoғyrlandyru</span><span><b>, e</b></span><span>mүmkіn sozylady retіnde aptasyna bіr de ekі ay. Eң aldymen baғa boyynsha altyn ghәne kүmіs қalady diapazonynda </span><span><b>1530-1580</b></span><span> ghәne </span><span><b>17.3-18.3</b></span><span> , tiіsіnshe, nauryz ayynyң ortasyna deyіn, eger әrine ghoқ priletit kezektі </span><span><i><b>"chernyy lebedy"</b></i></span><span>. </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Қalyp ghұmys іstey osy diapazonda, ras, bұғan ghylғy longa, ghay ғana </span><span><i><b>"өrt sөndіrushі"</b></i></span><span>. Өnerkәsіptіk metaldar tiіs fonynda ghalpy toқmeyіlsu қalpyna kelіp, baғalarda siyaқty, әrқashan mәsele palladiy.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Osy metall bolghau өte қiyn, bіraқ TMK " dedі. tapshylyғyn palladiy ghol bermeydі, sondyқtan ghaңa rekordtar bіz kөre almaymyz. </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Sauda diapazony altyn boyynsha </span><span><b>1548 – 1562,</b></span><span> boyynsha kүmіs </span><span><b>17,47 -17.83 </b></span><span>ghәne platine </span><span><b>965 - 992 </b></span><span><i>(baғa spot naryғyn ghәne olar erekshelenedі baғa fyyuchersterіn). </i></span></p><p><span><b>Boryshtyқ naryғy</b></span><span> – taңerteң kіrіstіlіgі boyynsha amerikandyқ bondam </span><span><b>10Y</b></span><span> (</span><span><i>onghyldyқ қaғaz</i></span><span>) deңgeyіnde </span><span><b>1.68%</b></span><span>, al </span><span><b>3M</b></span><span> (</span><span><i>үsh aylyқ kase</i></span><span>) </span><span><b>1.54%. Formalydy, қisyқ dohodnostey obligaciyalar boyynsha signaliziruet densaulyқ turaly, ekonomika, өytkenі inversiya bayқalady. </b></span><span>Bіraқ қol ghetkіzіldі, ol arқyly satyp alu FRGh қysқa merzіmdі obligaciyalar. Tabystylyғy boyynsha </span><span><b>30Y</b></span><span> (tridcatiletnim bondam) komandasy kөterіldі, қatysty keshegі kүnnen ghoғary deңgeyde bolady, bұl </span><span><b>2.16%. Sұranys tәuekelі – iterіp, baғasy obligaciyalar tөmen. </b></span></p><p><span> </span><span></span><a>https://www.vesti.ru/doc.html?id=3237002&amp;cid=6</a><span> </span></p><p><span> </span><span></span><a>https://www.marketwatch.com/story/china-to-cut-tariffs-in-half-on-75-billion-of-us-goods-2020-02-05?mod=home-page</a><span> </span></p><p><span> </span><span></span><a>https://bcs-express.ru/novosti-i-analitika/2020267520-chto-zhdat-ot-tsb-v-piatnitsu</a><span> </span></p><p><span> </span><span></span><a>https://www.zerohedge.com/economics/americans-express-record-high-optimism-personal-finances</a><span> </span></p><p><span><b>Dostar, eger Sіzge қiyn emes, maғan қoyyңyzdar laykter ghәne қaldyryңyz өz tүsіnіktemelerі. Bұl damytudaғy bіzdің arna osy resursynda ornalastyrylғan. Sіzge kөp-kөp rahmet.</b></span></p><blockquote><span><i>Ghazylyңyz bіzdің YOUTUBE, YANDEX ZEN ghәne TELEGRAM arnasy ForeksIndeksySyrye</i></span></blockquote><blockquote><span></span><a><i>www.youtube.com/channel/UC1N3tsoXdpGF24k7r1lKE6A/featured?disable_polymer=1</i></a></blockquote><blockquote><span></span><a><i>https://zen.yandex.ru/profile/editor/id/5cf556fe1b104c00afef7abd</i></a></blockquote><blockquote><span></span><a><i>t.me/ForexIndexCommodities</i></a></blockquote><blockquote><span><u><i><b>Қosylu үshіn aқyly sauda signaldary boyynsha BRENT markaly mұnaydyң nemese oқu үshіn sauda bіzdің ghүyesіnde</b></i></u></span><span><i> ghazyңyzdar bіzge poshtaғa </i></span><span></span><a><i><b>stocktrader7501@gmail.com</b></i></a><span> 